    "title": "Lechangxia",
    "excerpt":"Flooding is a constant issue in Lechangxia due to the heavy precipitation events, there is a dam for hydropower and flood mitigation in this catchment. LUC change induced by forestry is also obvious. This pilot may be used to study the joint impact of climate change, dam operation and LUC change. &lt;!–                                   –&gt;  ","url": "http://localhost:4000/Lechangxia-en/"
